803
00:51:19,744 --> 00:51:23,663
- This is Bergman!
- I like it. It's kind of nice.

804
00:51:23,831 --> 00:51:26,875
Pure, unadulterated Bergman!
It's beautiful!

805
00:51:27,001 --> 00:51:28,960
- Do you live here?
- Yeah, we do.

806
00:51:29,086 --> 00:51:31,212
We've been here
for quite a while.

807
00:51:31,338 --> 00:51:34,007
Lucky you! It's so gorgeous.
I've never seen...

808
00:51:34,175 --> 00:51:37,302
- Of course, the people are all wrong
for Bergman, aren't they?
