881
00:54:56,043 --> 00:54:57,794
but, uh...

882
00:54:57,920 --> 00:54:59,879
Walker thinks that...

883
00:55:00,047 --> 00:55:03,007
you'd make
a fine governor in this state.

884
00:55:03,133 --> 00:55:05,051
He thinks the time's right.

885
00:55:05,177 --> 00:55:07,261
He thinks the people
of Tennessee love you.

886
00:55:07,388 --> 00:55:10,556
He knows they do.
He knows how you feel about them.

887
00:55:10,724 --> 00:55:13,851
And he wants you
to know that...

888
00:55:13,978 --> 00:55:17,438
should the time come
you want to run...

889
00:55:17,564 --> 00:55:20,775
