900
00:55:45,759 --> 00:55:47,427
Terrific.

901
00:55:48,887 --> 00:55:52,056
- Is Haven around?
- Yeah, right around the corner.

902
00:55:52,182 --> 00:55:55,059
Would you check and see
if it's all right if we come?

903
00:55:55,185 --> 00:55:57,812
- Yeah.
- I see him with other people.
Thank you, Del.

904
00:55:57,938 --> 00:56:00,189
