- Aw.

1733
02:13:13,110 --> 02:13:16,946
- Can't you just call him,
tell him you're hung up?
- No, I can't.

1734
02:13:19,450 --> 02:13:22,077
- Couldn't you just stay another hour?
- No, no.

1735
02:13:28,584 --> 02:13:30,335
I just can't.

